{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would go to a movie with some friends and you'd see hordes of young people marching, singing the Horst Wessel song, you know, when Jewish blood spurts from knives.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was going on for at least two years before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no spare time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no spare time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had after-school activities, dance classes, ice skating classes, horseback riding classes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no spare time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what spare time there was, I would go to the various stores that my parents had and do my homework.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I just told you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my aunt and uncle, my father's sister, and their son left in 1934 for what was then Palestine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They saw it coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tried to get their money out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They lost 2/3 of their fortune by doing that, because it was not legal to take any money out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I begged my father to do that too and he wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He called my uncle the meshugganah Max, you know, the crazy Max, because he did that and lost so much money.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then my aunt came to visit from Palestine, crying bitterly how she hated it there and how hard it was and how terrible it was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my cousin didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she didn't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father forcively had to push her back on the train to take the ship back to Israel, which was then Palestine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They lived in Haifa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their name was Fellman, and my aunt Adele and my Uncle Max and my cousin Fritz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're all dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I saw him march into Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was on the Ringstrasse, which is the main thoroughfare in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It rings the inner city.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
